Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.84,0:01:48.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}カイト救出を誓った ゴンとキルア
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.84,0:01:48.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He knows exactly what we're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.33,0:01:50.85,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だが　ＮＧＬに戻るには
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.33,0:01:50.85,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We won't be able to trick him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.85,0:01:54.35,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}討伐隊を率いる ネテロ会長から出された
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.85,0:01:54.35,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What I felt after coming into \Ncontact with your Nen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.35,0:01:57.85,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ある条件をクリアしなければ ならなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.35,0:01:57.85,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}was not anger, fear, or hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.84,0:02:01.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何？　それ。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.84,0:02:01.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Only senses of duty and resolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.83,0:02:09.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}割り符だよ 印のついた竹や木の板切れを ２つに割って　互いに持つんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.83,0:02:09.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If you are fighting for the survival \Nof humanity, your battle is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.33,0:02:13.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}これで仲間の証しや 文書の証明にしたりする。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.33,0:02:13.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You need further explanation? It seems you doubt what you've just heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.37,0:02:18.87,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((最寄りの街に２人 刺客を放った))
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.37,0:02:18.87,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Then I shall repeat myself. You have won... The battle is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.85,0:02:26.35,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}今回の場合は　刺客が　それぞれ 片方の割り符を持っている。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.85,0:02:26.35,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The rest of what I have to \Nsay is for your ears only.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.35,0:02:30.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}倒して奪えってことだな。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.35,0:02:30.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The reason I am here is quite simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.83,0:02:44.85,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}消されてる。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.83,0:02:44.85,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That is really all I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.85,0:02:47.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}確認したってことだよな。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.85,0:02:47.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I desire nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.34,0:02:48.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うん。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.34,0:02:48.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}After coming into contact with your Nen, I learned my current state and fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.84,0:02:58.88,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あなた達が　キルアとゴンね。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.84,0:02:58.88,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And having learned my fate, I simply wish
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.88,0:03:01.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}はじめまして。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.88,0:03:01.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}to spend my remaining time with Komugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.84,0:03:06.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}私　パームって者です。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.84,0:03:06.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That is all I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.90,0:03:22.90,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}説明するわ お茶でも飲みましょう。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.90,0:03:22.90,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Was this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.84,0:03:30.85,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}私は　ノヴ先生の弟子なの。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.84,0:03:30.85,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Was this a plan you devised after \Ndiscovering my personality?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.85,0:03:34.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}先生には 足手まといだって言われたけど
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.85,0:03:34.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No, I already know the answer... It's impossible. You expect me to believe you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.84,0:03:38.86,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}無理やり　ついて来たの。 誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.84,0:03:38.86,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You think I'll just accept that explanation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:44.95,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}多分 ネテロ会長と　一緒にいた人だ。 そうそう　黒スーツの…。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:44.95,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}An omnipotent King would \Nnever lie to himself in order to fool a lower being like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.95,0:03:50.85,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}先生って素晴らしい人よ。 クールで　知的で　冷静で。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.95,0:03:50.85,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}After all the killing you have done, \Nand soon will do...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.85,0:03:54.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あっ　冷静は　クールと同じ意味ね やだわ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.85,0:03:54.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}A creature like you... The King admits defeat? Cares for a human?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.34,0:03:57.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あっ　でも　尊敬してるだけよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.34,0:03:57.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Impossible! That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.32,0:04:00.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}別に恋愛感情は…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.32,0:04:00.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He's doing this because it is the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.84,0:04:06.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ない… とは言い切れないかも　ウフフ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.84,0:04:06.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I believe it was only a slight change...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:08.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だって　大切だものね。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:08.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.34,0:04:15.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}相手を尊敬できるかどうかって 恋愛に。 あっ　もちろん こんなこと　先生は知らないわよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.34,0:04:15.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Something, somewhere, changed ever so slightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.84,0:04:23.87,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何も言ってないし…　これからも。 うわぁ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.84,0:04:23.87,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}In my current state, I am not a god, but I... No...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.44,0:04:32.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ゲフっ。 分からないわよね 先のことなんて。 だって　だって　恋愛って
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.44,0:04:32.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Perhaps, I only feel this way \Nbecause everything has fallen into place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.34,0:04:35.35,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}突然　発展するものじゃない？ そう思わない？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.34,0:04:35.35,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You should know I have very little time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.35,0:04:39.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}えと　ちょっと　いい？ 俺達　戦うんだよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.35,0:04:39.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I want you to tell me her location, so I do not have to search for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.33,0:04:45.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}えっ　あっ　やだわ そうよね　ごめんなさい。 会長と先生に
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.33,0:04:45.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What are you saying?! Stop this... Yes, I know where she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:50.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}これ以上の同伴は 絶対ダメって言われて。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:50.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Why don't you just torture it out of me? I know the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.83,0:04:54.85,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}でも　私　食い下がったの 絶対行くって。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.83,0:04:54.85,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We both know that isn't an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.85,0:05:03.42,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}一生分　話したんじゃないか ってぐらい 自分の熱意をアピールしたわ。 そしたら　条件付きで 許してくれたの　フフフ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.85,0:05:03.42,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Your aura is as strong and beautiful \Nas any I have ever beheld. Stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.42,0:05:09.85,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}いや　だから…。 先生ね　冷たく見えるけど ホントは　とても優しいのよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.42,0:05:09.85,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}All I can do is to ask you to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:32.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あの２人　下品で野蛮で 口のきき方も知らない クソガキどもが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:32.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I am part Ant now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.82,0:05:40.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}私を差し置いて ＮＧＬに行くなんて 許せる？　いや無理。 うわ！ パームさん！　「発」止めて　「発」！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.82,0:05:40.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I know very well how important \Nyou are to the race...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.43,0:05:46.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}この人　俺と同じ強化系だ 何か　やだな…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.43,0:05:46.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Not that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.83,0:05:50.35,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ナックルとシュート？ 俺達じゃなくて？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.83,0:05:50.35,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Don't go to such lengths...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.35,0:05:57.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そうよ。 だって　ナックルとシュートを 倒すのは　私じゃなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.35,0:05:57.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You mustn't do that... I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.34,0:05:59.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あなた達だから。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.34,0:05:59.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But on one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.36,0:06:04.86,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ナックルとシュートは モラウさんの弟子よ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.36,0:06:04.86,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}May I use my power
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.84,0:06:12.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}内容は分からないけど　とにかく
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.84,0:06:12.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}to watch your final moments with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.84,0:06:19.35,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ＮＧＬに行けるのは 私達か彼らか どちらか　ひと組だけ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.84,0:06:19.35,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If that is what it takes to be with Komugi, you certainly may.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:27.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}１か月間 割り符を手放すなってことは
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:27.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Sorry, Killua...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.84,0:06:32.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}誰かが奪いに来るってことだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.84,0:06:32.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I couldn't keep our promise...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.85,0:07:26.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}男子たるもの　敵に 背を向けたりするんじゃねえぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.85,0:07:26.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}4-7-1, marshal...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:34.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まっ　場所が分かっても 行かないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:34.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Wake up, Komugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.84,0:07:39.35,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ありゃ　おとりだな　もう１人が どこかで見張ってるはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.84,0:07:39.35,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's time to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:51.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}パームの話だと　相手は　俺達の 名前すら知らないらしいからな。 うん。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:51.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We have a shocking news update.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.34,0:07:53.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何とかして俺達を あぶり出す気だろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.34,0:07:53.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The true purpose of the summoning
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.83,0:07:59.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}本気で　あんなことするバカは いないよ。 そいつ　強そうだった？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.83,0:07:59.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}of all Republic of East Gorteau \Ncitizens to the capital city
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.83,0:08:01.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}かなりな。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.83,0:08:01.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}was a plot by the Supreme \NLeader to massacre them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.85,0:08:09.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}どのくらいで倒せると思う？ そりゃ分かんねえよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.85,0:08:09.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The body of Supreme Leader Diego \Nwas discovered under the rubble, suggesting that the victims were \Nlikely forced into mass suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.34,0:08:20.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}会長の連れにも言われたけど 「念」の戦いに絶対なんてないしな。 ただ　そいつに言わせると 俺の勝ち目って考え方が ズレてるらしいけど
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.34,0:08:20.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But the second-in-command, \NSecretary Bizeff, is still missing, so some authorities believe a \Nrevolution is the greater likelihood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.84,0:08:23.36,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺は　そうは思わない。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.84,0:08:23.36,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Meanwhile, there has also been trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.36,0:08:27.43,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}勝つ確率を上げなきゃ 生き残れるわけがないんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.36,0:08:27.43,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}in the NGL region of the Mitene Union, \Nas international peacekeepers
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.43,0:08:31.43,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}相手と自分との力量を測るのは 重要な作業だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.43,0:08:31.43,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}have sent queries regarding refugees, and have received no response.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:37.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}仮に１００回　戦ったとして １２回しか勝てないんじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:37.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There have been rumors of
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.84,0:08:39.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}論外だからな。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.84,0:08:39.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}illicit dealings between \NEast Gorteau and NGL, and the international community \Nseeks to use this incident
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.34,0:08:48.35,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}最低でも５割。 できれば７割以上の勝算が欲しい。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.34,0:08:48.35,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}as an opportunity to conduct \Na more forceful investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.35,0:08:52.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そのために俺達が しなきゃならないことは　２つ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.35,0:08:52.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yeah, the boss did his duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.94,0:08:58.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}少しでも基礎能力を上げることと 相手の能力を知ること。 うん。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.94,0:08:58.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No, I wasn't there to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.84,0:09:00.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}相手の能力さえ分かれば
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.84,0:09:00.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It still isn't clear yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.83,0:09:06.35,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ゲンスルーの時みたく 対策が立てやすい。 うん…。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.83,0:09:06.35,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yeah, we're waiting on Palm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:09.35,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}半分賛成　半分反対。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:09.35,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Can we really trust her alone to verify the King's death?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.35,0:09:13.91,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}どういうことだ？ 基礎能力を上げるのは　俺も賛成。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.35,0:09:13.91,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Plus, that person was captured and converted by the enemy, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.91,0:09:17.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}でも　相手の能力は 知らなくていいと思う。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.91,0:09:17.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Well, that's a question of professionalism.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.83,0:09:19.85,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}はぁ？　何でだよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.83,0:09:19.85,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It would be professional
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.85,0:09:23.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それじゃ　リスクが高くなるだけで 何もいいこと　ねえだろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.85,0:09:23.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}to provide a complete report \Nin the safest manner possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.83,0:09:29.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}でも　それが普通でしょ ＮＧＬでの戦いはさ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.83,0:09:29.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But those are the professionals who spend all of their time sitting in fully-furnished offices.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.32,0:09:33.38,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺達の目的は　ナックル達を 倒すことじゃなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.32,0:09:33.38,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And when we field Hunters are told \Nto trust a partner, we trust them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.38,0:09:37.88,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}強くなってＮＧＬに戻り カイトを助けること。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.38,0:09:37.88,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We're all professionals... But I'm the one out in the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.85,0:09:47.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}つまり　どんな敵か 分からない状況で戦っても 勝てるっていう強さがいるんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.85,0:09:47.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The Vice Chairman's faction won't \Naccept that argument.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.32,0:09:50.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}下準備が必要な勝ち方なんて 意味ないよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.32,0:09:50.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If they find out, you can expect \Nto be questioned, at the least.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.84,0:10:15.40,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}なっ！ どわ！ バカか　お前は！ あっ！ あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.84,0:10:15.40,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Uh, I am Netero...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.40,0:10:19.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ビスケ！ ふむ。 何で　ここに？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.40,0:10:19.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Chairman, thank you for a job well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.32,0:10:23.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}私が呼んだの。 えっ？　まさか知り合い？ えっ？　まさか知り合い？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.32,0:10:23.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}May you rest in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.83,0:10:30.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}いいえ　あなた達のこと 調べただけよ。 どうやって？ だって　ビスケとは…。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.83,0:10:30.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The same day, a video was streamed \Nonline in which Netero announced
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.33,0:10:39.37,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}フフフ…　私の能力を使えば 容易なことよ。 さぁ　時間が惜しいわ 開始しましょう。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.33,0:10:39.37,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}his resignation as Chairman \Nof the Hunter Association, and gave instructions for \Nchoosing his successor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.84,0:10:45.85,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}モラウの厮徒抹殺計画。 イヤです。 イヤです。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.84,0:10:45.85,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}However, major news stories in the \Ngovernment-run media overshadowed it, and only a few realized that \Nthe video was his will.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.31,0:10:52.81,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それじゃあ　始めようか。 オス！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.31,0:10:52.81,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Now, let us drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.81,0:10:55.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}痛っ！　何すんのさ　いきなり！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.81,0:10:55.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Let us drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.82,0:10:58.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}さっきの続きだよ バカか　お前は！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.82,0:10:58.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Drink to the human race.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.82,0:11:05.81,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あのジジイはね 人が悪いんで有名なんだわさ。 )
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.82,0:11:05.81,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}In every age, there will be good \Nhumans and bad humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.81,0:11:14.80,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あいつが １か月でやれっていうのは 本当なら　１年かけても 達成困難なことだったりするの！ １週間で 何とかなるわけないでしょ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.81,0:11:14.80,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Human life is too long \Nto devote to reproduction, yet too short to devote to learning, \Nin the helix of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.80,0:11:21.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}でも俺達は　一刻も早く戻って カイトを助けなきゃいけないんだ。 何の話だい？　それ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.80,0:11:21.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Perhaps that is why humans succumb \Nto desire and seek release.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.32,0:11:32.80,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}楽しかったねぇ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.32,0:11:32.80,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Despite the fact that life is complete \Nwith the sun, the land, and poetry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.81,0:11:43.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もう一度したいなぁ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.81,0:11:43.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's over...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.31,0:12:05.87,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}さすが　年の功… 説教慣れしてやがる 分かったかい？ オス…。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.31,0:12:05.87,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But it feels like we \Nhaven't played in ages...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.87,0:12:08.37,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}んじゃ　特訓開始だわさ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.87,0:12:08.37,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Playing in real life is completely different \Nthan playing in my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.82,0:12:14.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まずは…　「練」！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.82,0:12:14.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yes. I thought I felt someone kick \Nme hard in the stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.30,0:12:20.80,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}その状態を３時間　維持すること。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.30,0:12:20.80,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}After that, a strange person kidnapped me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.30,0:12:24.85,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}キルア　どのくらい　いける？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.30,0:12:24.85,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But you must have saved me, Supreme Leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.85,0:12:28.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}調子がいい時で 最高５５分くらいかな。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.85,0:12:28.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It wasn't me. It was my subordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.83,0:12:31.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}これが　できなきゃ 次には進まない。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.83,0:12:31.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I was wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.31,0:12:35.81,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}死ぬ気でやんなさいな　ホホホ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.31,0:12:35.81,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I jumped to the wrong conclusion. I was unworthy of their loyalty...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.80,0:12:42.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ハァ…　うっ　うぅ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.80,0:12:42.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}When they stop by, I must thank them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:45.89,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ハァ　ハァ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:45.89,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I will relay your gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.89,0:12:48.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ぐっ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.89,0:12:48.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'll be seeing them soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.81,0:12:56.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何だい １時間も　たってないわよさ。 はいはい　続けて！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.81,0:12:56.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I know. Let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.30,0:12:58.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}くっ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.30,0:12:58.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.30,0:13:01.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うぅ…　くっ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.30,0:13:01.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Once, you asked my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.82,0:13:06.80,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「練」を１０分間延ばすだけでも １か月かかるっていわれるのよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.82,0:13:06.80,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Y-Yes... My name is Meruem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:09.80,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}寝てる暇なんか ありゃしないわさ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:09.80,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Meruem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.81,0:13:18.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}おのれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.81,0:13:18.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Meruem-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.32,0:13:24.38,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}臆したか　腰抜けが！ てめぇら　死刑確定！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.32,0:13:24.38,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}M-My name is Komugi... It is an honor to know you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.82,0:13:40.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}首輪してるじゃねえかよ どこだ　飼い主はよ。 公園はキレイに使わなきゃ ダメじゃねえか　まったく…。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.82,0:13:40.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I knew nothing. I didn't understand what really mattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.85,0:13:46.35,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}明日は　３０分後スタートよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.85,0:13:46.35,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No honorific is necessary. Don't make me repeat myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.81,0:13:56.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ようやく　私の力が 必要となる時が来たわね。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.81,0:13:56.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I would never dare address \Nyou without an honorific! Then if I beat you at Gungi, you will \Naddress me without the honorific.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.31,0:14:17.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}さぁ　頼むわさ　クッキィちゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.31,0:14:17.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There is no need for you to die. I am not the same person I was before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.82,0:14:23.81,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「まじかるエステ」！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.82,0:14:23.81,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You should be prepared to lose. Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.81,0:14:26.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「ピアノマッサージ」。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.81,0:14:26.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What do you want if you win?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.36,0:14:30.90,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}フフっ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.36,0:14:30.90,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I would like another match!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.82,0:14:38.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}こんなこと言うの失礼ですけど やり方は　お任せします。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.82,0:14:38.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It was a foolish question. Let's begin, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.30,0:14:42.81,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あなたは　私の力が選んだ 答えなのだから。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.30,0:14:42.81,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}1-5-1, marshal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.81,0:14:46.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}でも もしも１か月で　この２人が
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.81,0:14:46.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}9-9-1, marshal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.83,0:14:50.90,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}モラウの厮徒を倒すことが できなかったら
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.83,0:14:50.90,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}7-9-1, pawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.90,0:14:55.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}私…　自分を抑える自信が ありません。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.90,0:14:55.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}2-3-1, pawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.32,0:14:58.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}私は　どうしても ＮＧＬに行きたいのです。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.32,0:14:58.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}2-7-2, musketeer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:15:01.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ホントなら　今すぐにでも。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:15:01.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.31,0:15:04.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それなのに　我慢して　我慢して 我慢して　我慢して
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.31,0:15:04.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}7-1-2, fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.31,0:15:07.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}我慢した揚げ句　ダメだったら…。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.31,0:15:07.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This is... Marshal ...kokoriko?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.32,0:15:13.41,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}きっと　あなた達を殺すわ。 それ　脅し？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.32,0:15:13.41,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Komugi, do you mean to mock me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.41,0:15:17.81,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}いいえ　忠告です あなた達が心配なの。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.41,0:15:17.81,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No. I want a sincere answer. I will not allow you to fool around.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.81,0:15:23.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だから　もし　ダメだと思うなら 早めに　ここから 立ち去ってほしいの。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.81,0:15:23.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yes, I have never fooled around \Nwhile playing Gungi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.30,0:15:31.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そのほうが　今までの経験上 私の怒りは少なくて済むわ。 それって　私に言うのは　お門違い。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.30,0:15:31.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Very well. If you lose, you will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.82,0:15:34.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}その子達が起きたら 言ってあげなさいな。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.82,0:15:34.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.81,0:15:40.80,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}大丈夫！　任せといて！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.81,0:15:40.80,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Is she saying this will not \Nmean her certain death?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.80,0:15:44.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}絶対　パームさんを ＮＧＬに連れて行くから！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.80,0:15:44.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}She had a number of other options.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.30,0:15:46.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だから　パームさんも 気づいたことがあったら
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.30,0:15:46.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But all would only serve to lengthen the
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.79,0:15:49.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}どんどん教えてね　頑張るよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.79,0:15:49.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}game without increasing her chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.85,0:15:56.85,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ああいう子よ　信じてあげて。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.85,0:15:56.85,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}9-2-1, new lieutenant general.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.32,0:16:17.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}これからの１か月 会長達は何する気？　ねぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.32,0:16:17.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}4-6-2, spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.82,0:16:22.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}えっ？　あっ　えっと…。 「探り」と「削り」って 言ってましたね。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.82,0:16:22.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.30,0:16:30.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}王が生まれるまでの タイムリミットについては
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.30,0:16:30.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}She
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.82,0:16:37.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}専門家の間でも 意見が分かれるところなので…。 最短で　あと２か月という 見解に合わせて
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.82,0:16:37.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}has found a way out. That night, I realized something. Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.82,0:16:40.38,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}行動して行くそうです。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.82,0:16:40.38,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Let me think.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.30,0:16:51.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あいつ　わしより強くねぇ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.30,0:16:51.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Here. This is the only way to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.30,0:16:56.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}会長より強いですって？ ご冗談を。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.30,0:16:56.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I should be able to checkmate her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.31,0:16:59.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それが本当なら ハンターは　誰一人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.31,0:16:59.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}When she's forced closer to my position, \Nmy advantage grows with each move.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.31,0:17:09.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}太刀打ちできない 道理になってしまう。 ホッ　わしが念使いで 最強だったのは 半世紀以上も昔の話じゃよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.31,0:17:09.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But if she slows down and allows \Nme a turn to attack, she can't stop the knight \Nand lieutenant general!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.31,0:17:10.81,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}今じゃ　お主らと
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.31,0:17:10.81,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}2-6-1, knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.81,0:17:13.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}どっこいどっこいといった ところじゃろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.81,0:17:13.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I reversed her new move!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.79,0:17:16.80,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それならば　十分にお強い。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.79,0:17:16.80,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.32,0:17:22.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}全盛期の半分以下かも しれんのにか？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.32,0:17:22.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What is wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.32,0:17:25.35,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}年は　とりたくないのう。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.32,0:17:25.35,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Why do you cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.35,0:17:27.91,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}口の減らない人だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.35,0:17:27.91,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Am I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.91,0:17:29.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}でも　やるんでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.91,0:17:29.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Am I allowed
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.83,0:17:33.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}できれば　御免被りたいがな。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.83,0:17:33.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}to be so happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.30,0:17:37.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}やらずに済めば それに越したことはない。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.30,0:17:37.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Can...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.32,0:17:46.38,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}わしらの標的は 女王のみじゃからな。 まっ　あの「円」の監視を かいくぐるのは　至難。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.32,0:17:46.38,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Can so many wonderful things happen to someone like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.31,0:17:57.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}問題は　いかにして 勝つかじゃが…。 妙案があれば　賜りたいのう。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.31,0:17:57.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I suppose I must tell you the truth. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.82,0:18:04.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まったく　人が悪い。 答えは　私達を呼んだ時点で 出ているんでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.82,0:18:04.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I have been poisoned, and I have little time. Meruem-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.38,0:18:11.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}静かに　１匹ずつ 消して行きましょう。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.38,0:18:11.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Komugi, I wanted... to spend my final moments \Nplaying against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.31,0:18:38.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まぁ　じっくり行きましょうや。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.31,0:18:38.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Meruem-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.79,0:18:42.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}どうせやるなら　楽しまなきゃな。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.79,0:18:42.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Right now, I am very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.30,0:18:49.35,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}さて　まずは　敵の数ぐらいは 知らなきゃな。 行け！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.30,0:18:49.35,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I may not be worthy, but please allow me to join you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.81,0:18:56.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うん？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.81,0:18:56.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.32,0:19:03.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}大勢だ　何か来る
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.32,0:19:03.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I believe
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.30,0:19:08.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}生物じゃないな 敵の力かな？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.30,0:19:08.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}that I was born to be here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.32,0:19:16.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}さて　どうするかニャ 待ってて構わないだろう ニャ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.32,0:19:16.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}...was born for this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.86,0:20:53.80,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あの夢のような時間を…)) )
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.86,0:20:53.80,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}4-4-1, pawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.80,0:21:00.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.80,0:21:00.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}6-5-1, knight. 2-7-2, new spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.84,0:21:03.89,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ダハ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.84,0:21:03.89,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Komugi, are you still there? Yes, I sure am.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.89,0:21:06.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ハァ　ハァ　ハァ…。 ハァ　ハァ　ハァ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.89,0:21:06.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.31,0:21:11.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ほらほら　何やってんの！ そんなんじゃ キメラアントどころか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.31,0:21:11.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}4-5-1, lieutenant general.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.31,0:21:13.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ナックルとシュートにも 勝てやしないよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.31,0:21:13.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That's checkmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.82,0:21:16.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ＮＧＬ行きは　諦めるのかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.82,0:21:16.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Komugi, are you still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.30,0:21:21.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}誰が…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.30,0:21:21.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yes, yes... Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.34,0:21:23.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}諦めるか！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.34,0:21:23.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Let's play another match. The loser goes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.91,0:21:26.80,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺達は　どんなことをしたって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.91,0:21:26.80,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Komugi... Yes, yes? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.80,0:21:33.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ＮＧＬに 戻らなきゃならないんだ！ うお！ うお！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.80,0:21:33.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It appears I never defeated \Nyou a single time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.79,0:21:39.29,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}カイトを助けるために！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.79,0:21:39.29,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We've just gotten started! Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.40,0:21:49.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}再会したビスケによって 再び始まった修行の日々
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.40,0:21:49.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}1-5-1, marshal. 9-5-1, marshal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.82,0:21:51.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}目的は　ただ一つ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.82,0:21:51.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Komugi, are you still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.79,0:21:55.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}カイトを助けるために 強くなること
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.79,0:21:55.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.31,0:21:59.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}その強い思いが ゴンを突き動かしていた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.31,0:21:59.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's your turn, Meruem-sama. I'm a little tired...
